1 Kentucky:
2 Section 1. The Senate hereby honors and remembers the life and sacrifice of
3 Staff Sergeant Benjamin Pennington, who paid the ultimate price in service to our nation.
4 Section 2. When the Senate adjourns this day, it does so in honor and loving
5 memory of Staff Sergeant Benjamin Pennington.
6 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
7 Resolution to Senator Matthew Deneen for presentation to the family.
